Recommended:
Racemenu - Overlays Pugin

Installation: Just unpack the jslot file at data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets
This preset based on imperial race, so it works mostly on human races specialy on imperial.You have to use console command: showracemenu - to enter character generation section, after that,select the preset tab, press F9 for load presets and click on LadyDragon.jslot
